                            <li>Ideal age of student - 8 years or above</li>
                            <li>Interest in music and learning the instrument + willingness to practice regularly</li>
                            <li>Student must have their own Tabla, so that they can practice and hone their skills</li>
                        </ul>
                        <ul class="mt-4 list">
                            <h4 class="fw-bold">Topic Covered</h4>
                            <li>Introduction to Tabla</li>
                            <li>Posture, fingers and hand positioning</li>
                            <li>Knowledge of basic rhythm patterns</li>
                            <li>Introduction to Sam, Taali, Khaali and Laya</li>
                            <li>Basic Kaydas, Tihais in Teentaal, </li>
                            <li>Concept of Dugun, Tigun</li>
                            <li>Basic Dadra, Keherwa Cycles and Recitation</li>
                            <li>History of Tabla and life of famous Tabla players</li>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <aside style="width:30%" class="mx-4">
