                                <p class="aside-info-p fs-6"
                                    style="background-image: url('https://a.storyblok.com/f/114532/48x48/75ddd6f2d5/medal-star.png/m/');">
                                    Certificate on completion</p>
                                <p class="aside-info-p fs-6"
                                    style="background-image: url('https://a.storyblok.com/f/114532/48x48/1d14956dde/calendar-2.png/m/'); ">
                                    Duration: 6-8 months</p>
                            </div>

                            <a class="btn btn-outline-dark fw-bold w-100 mb-2 p-2 text-decoration-none" href="#packages"
                                id="link1" data-link="packages">See Packages</a><br>
                            <a href="/tablaCourseBeg" class="btn btn-warning  fw-bold w-100 p-2">Book Now</a>
                        </div>

                    </aside>
                    <aside class="mt-5 border border-secondary-subtle rounded-3">
                        <div class="px-5">
                            <h4 class="mt-4 fw-bold">Related Courses</h4>
                            <div>
                                <p class="aside-info-p mt-3 py-3 rounded-4"
                                    style="padding-left:70px;background-position: 10% 50%; background-image: url('https://a.storyblok.com/f/114532/48x48/3d57a2f033/layer.png/m/');">
                                    <a class="text-decoration-none text-dark a-font" href="">Shruti-Sangam Sitar Course
                                        Part 1</a>
                                </p>
                                <p class="aside-info-p mt-3 py-3 rounded-4"
                                    style="padding-left:70px;background-position: 10% 50%; background-image: url('https://a.storyblok.com/f/114532/48x48/3d57a2f033/layer.png/m/');">
                                    <a class="text-decoration-none text-dark a-font" href="">Shruti-Sangam Flute Course
                                        Part 1</a>
                                </p>
                                <p class="aside-info-p mt-3 py-3 rounded-4"
                                    style="padding-left:70px;background-position: 10% 50%; background-image: url('https://a.storyblok.com/f/114532/48x48/3d57a2f033/layer.png/m/');">
                                    <a class="text-decoration-none text-dark a-font" href="">Shruti-Sangam Harmonium
                                        Course Part 1</a>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
        <article id="packages" class="my-5">
            <div class="sec-div">
                <h2 class="text-center text-dark my-5 fw-bold">Your Packages</h2>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="border border-secondary-subtle p-4 rounded-4 mx-2">
                        <div>
                            <span class="p-2 px-4 fw-bold span1">6 Months</span>
